{"tid":376723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共151名消防及救護員拯救被困飛鵝山男女","createTime":"2017-08-27T07:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T09:42:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d76617b6b21963ab90309f94e28b2e81b9fbeb5f","tid":376723,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"一對男女昨晚在飛鵝山發射站行山，滑落崖底被困。消防九龍中區指揮官姜世明表示，女事主頭和腿部受傷，需要擔架床才能抬離現場，一名消防隊目在搜救過程中滑倒受傷。直至下午2時，消防共派出30 架次消防車，9架救護車，共151名消防及救護員拯救。<br />\n<br />\n姜世明表示，昨晚約7時許接報後，已派出攀山拯救專隊協助拯救，至晚上9時許，已確定兩人位置，到晚上11時找到被困的男女。消防先用繩固定位置，再用斗篷築起臨時避雨點，等候早上高空拯救專隊出動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1350802-20170827.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1350802-20170827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ABAp%2BiCMwl6VFSawRmSdZaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=32b6f37f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1350802-20170827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cdcb205b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1350802-20170827.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"451cb4cc33df19d9deb0badb0e69a0fce583d453","tid":376723,"uid":67201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以叫佢地比翻啲人力物力錢"},{"pid":"b6ab4246d54a96e03bba9ce9ce5f4680ede4b6bc","tid":376723,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef2f8053a0dccefaa89b105f4e3b0a861edf10bf","tid":376723,"uid":45582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"事主為內地人"},{"pid":"012cd626536b33dd2043c2db0375866007a31098","tid":376723,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/22/221743_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://